Overwiev
Vetapp is backend solution for vetclinic operations .This API is designed using java Springboot
architecture for handling essential clinic operations like appointments, patient management, doctor schedules, and more.

In Doctor Controller you can manage such operations as:
-adding
-fire him(soft delete)
-getting by id
-getting all of doctors in list

In Patient controller you can :
- adding
-checking by id
-getting all in list

In appointment controller you can:
-check for availability based on medical and species specialization
-you are able to create a new appointment
-confirming or canceling appointment

Also all not confirmed appointmets are cleaned every hour from schedules.